covering Sun Ra or are among the legion of poets, artists, intellectuals, and musicians who consider him a spiritual godfather—will find that, indeed, space is the place.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 0aComposerszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aComposerszUnited StatesxBiography. 0aJazz musicianszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aJazz musicianszUnited StatesxBiography. 0aJazzxHistory and criticism. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Jazz.2bisacsh1 aCampbell, Robert L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978147801205440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478012054423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478012054/original  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles